Description:
DREAM HOME ON DAKOTA
Located in the ever-appealing Park Central Estate, the property at Dakota Street is centrally located. Walking distance to Maranatha School, Officer Train Station and Beaconsfield shopping precinct. This impeccable home offers:
- Master bedroom with walk in robe and ensuite;
- Remaining two bedrooms with built in robes;
- Tiled open plan kitchen, dining & living area;
- Ducted heating and evaporative cooling throughout;
- Alarm system;
- Double lock up garage with remote & separate lane way access;
- Courtyard for entertaining.
This quality family residence positioned on fantastic 238sqm allotment will appeal to retirees/down sizers, investors or those looking for their first home. You wont be disappointed with Dakota Street.

"ROSES ARE RED BUT LAVENDER IS BETTER"
"When presentation matters..."
You think the photos look good? Wait until you see it in person.
Located in the Lavender Estate just off Rix Road is an incredible home. Stunning presentation and functionally perfect for the modern day family.
The property features:
- 4 bedrooms with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Theatre room;
- Open plan living and dining room;
- Modern kitchen with walk-in pantry and a ton of bench space;
- Ducted heating and evaporative cooling;
- Under roof line alfresco;
- Double car garage with remote and internal access;
- Low-maintenance block with manicured landscaping.
View now before it's gone :)

WAKE UP TO WAKEHURST
"It's Timbertop and it's on one of the biggest blocks you're likely to find in the estate."
By now you know Timbertop is Officer's premier estate. The captivating community is friendly, inviting and best of all it's waiting for you.
Located within walking distance to public transport and shops plus very close to the proposed primary school set to open in two years.
The property is set on one of the larger Timbertop blocks. Exceeding 500sqm, the property is situated on the corner Wakehurst Road and has the potential for side access for anyone needing added vehicle space.
The house itself is contemporary and features:
- 3 bedrooms plus a study that if needed can be converted to a 4th bedroom;
- Master bedroom with glamorous en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Large formal living area;
- Open plan living/dining zone;
- Massive kitchen with walk-in pantry and 900mm stainless steal appliances;
- Central heating;
- Security alarms;
- Recently landscaped yard;
- Alfresco.
